Text.SourceString: Music makes everything better. You know what I mean?
Text.LocalizedString: Music makes everything better. You know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: I wonder what life will be like when I’m an adult.
Text.LocalizedString: I wonder what life will be like when I’m an adult.

Text.SourceString: I wish weekends lasted longer. Two days isn’t enough for recovery.
Text.LocalizedString: I wish weekends lasted longer. Two days isn’t enough for recovery.

Text.SourceString: I feel like I need more sleep than the average human.
Text.LocalizedString: I feel like I need more sleep than the average human.

Text.SourceString: I can’t decide if I’m more tired or more hungry. Probably both.
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t decide if I’m more tired or more hungry. Probably both.

Text.SourceString: Seriously, {ParentLabel}, considering becoming a pro gamer. Seems like the dream, right?
Text.LocalizedString: Seriously, {ParentLabel}, considering becoming a pro gamer. Seems like the dream, right?

Text.SourceString: I don’t get why I have to learn algebra. When will I ever use this?
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t get why I have to learn algebra. When will I ever use this?

Text.SourceString: Why does time drag in class but fly when I'm doing something fun?
Text.LocalizedString: Why does time drag in class but fly when I'm doing something fun?

Text.SourceString: I don’t get why people say high school is the best time of your life... It’s not.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t get why people say high school is the best time of your life... It’s not.

Text.SourceString: Oh, what should I have for lunch?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, what should I have for lunch?

Text.SourceString: Oh, what should I have for lunch?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, what should I have for lunch?

Text.SourceString: I’m starving. Is there anything good to snack on around here?
Text.LocalizedString: I’m starving. Is there anything good to snack on around here?

Text.SourceString: I was up way too late watching shows last night. Totally worth it, though!//<portrait=concerned>Please don't tell {SpouseLabel}!
Text.LocalizedString: I was up way too late watching shows last night. Totally worth it, though!//<portrait=concerned>Please don't tell {SpouseLabel}!

Text.SourceString: I still have no idea what I want to do when I grow up...does anyone actually figure that out?
Text.LocalizedString: I still have no idea what I want to do when I grow up...does anyone actually figure that out?

Text.SourceString: I might just travel the world when I’m older. Imagine all the cool places I could see.//Are you cool with that, {ParentLabel}?
Text.LocalizedString: I might just travel the world when I’m older. Imagine all the cool places I could see.//Are you cool with that, {ParentLabel}?

Text.SourceString: I kinda wanna do something creative, like design video games or something.
Text.LocalizedString: I kinda wanna do something creative, like design video games or something.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I think about becoming a vet.//<portrait=happy>I’d get to work with animals all day, which sounds awesome.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I think about becoming a vet.//<portrait=happy>I’d get to work with animals all day, which sounds awesome.

Text.SourceString: Spring is awesome—everything feels new and fresh again!
Text.LocalizedString: Spring is awesome—everything feels new and fresh again!

Text.SourceString: No more freezing mornings. Thank goodness!
Text.LocalizedString: No more freezing mornings. Thank goodness!

Text.SourceString: I feel like Spring is the season where I get the most energy. Why do you think, {ParentLabel}?//Maybe it's the sunshine.
Text.LocalizedString: I feel like Spring is the season where I get the most energy. Why do you think, {ParentLabel}?//Maybe it's the sunshine.

Text.SourceString: The Summer heat is insane... I’m melting over here!
Text.LocalizedString: The Summer heat is insane... I’m melting over here!

Text.SourceString: I love Summer, but I wouldn’t mind if it was, like, 10 degrees cooler.
Text.LocalizedString: I love Summer, but I wouldn’t mind if it was, like, 10 degrees cooler.

Text.SourceString: The heat’s worth it if it means beach days and no school!
Text.LocalizedString: The heat’s worth it if it means beach days and no school!

Text.SourceString: Can we plant some melons in our farm, {ParentLabel}?
Text.LocalizedString: Can we plant some melons in our farm, {ParentLabel}?

Text.SourceString: Fall is my favorite season—cool weather, cozy sweaters, and Spooky Festival!
Text.LocalizedString: Fall is my favorite season—cool weather, cozy sweaters, and Spooky Festival!

Text.SourceString: Let’s grow pumpkins this year! I really wanna carve a few.
Text.LocalizedString: Let’s grow pumpkins this year! I really wanna carve a few.

Text.SourceString: {SpouseLabel} is pretty cool...most of the time, anyway.
Text.LocalizedString: {SpouseLabel} is pretty cool...most of the time, anyway.

Text.SourceString: {SpouseLabel} said I could stay up late tonight. Please tell me you agree!
Text.LocalizedString: {SpouseLabel} said I could stay up late tonight. Please tell me you agree!

Text.SourceString: I think I get my sense of humor from {SpouseLabel}. It’s definitely not from you, {ParentLabel}!
Text.LocalizedString: I think I get my sense of humor from {SpouseLabel}. It’s definitely not from you, {ParentLabel}!

Text.SourceString: {SpouseLabel} makes the best pancakes.
Text.LocalizedString: {SpouseLabel} makes the best pancakes.

Text.SourceString: You always have the best ideas, {ParentLabel}.
Text.LocalizedString: You always have the best ideas, {ParentLabel}.

Text.SourceString: You always seem so calm, {ParentLabel}, even when things get crazy. I wish I could be more like that.
Text.LocalizedString: You always seem so calm, {ParentLabel}, even when things get crazy. I wish I could be more like that.

Text.SourceString: You're pretty cool, {ParentLabel}. I love you and {SpouseLabel} so much.
Text.LocalizedString: You're pretty cool, {ParentLabel}. I love you and {SpouseLabel} so much.

Text.SourceString: Winter’s great if you like freezing your toes off...which I don’t.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter’s great if you like freezing your toes off...which I don’t.

Text.SourceString: I don’t know why people get excited about snow. It's just cold and wet.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t know why people get excited about snow. It's just cold and wet.

Text.SourceString: If it wasn’t for how cold it is, Winter would be the perfect season. I mean, holidays, right?
Text.LocalizedString: If it wasn’t for how cold it is, Winter would be the perfect season. I mean, holidays, right?

Text.SourceString: I’ll admit, the snow looks really pretty this year.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ll admit, the snow looks really pretty this year.

Text.SourceString: It's so cold...I want some pizza please.
Text.LocalizedString: It's so cold...I want some pizza please.

Text.SourceString: It’s a bit gloomy today. But hey, at least the plants are happy!
Text.LocalizedString: It’s a bit gloomy today. But hey, at least the plants are happy!

Text.SourceString: Rain again?
Text.LocalizedString: Rain again?

Text.SourceString: I guess we won’t need to water the crops today!
Text.LocalizedString: I guess we won’t need to water the crops today!

Text.SourceString: Snow is pretty to look at.
Text.LocalizedString: Snow is pretty to look at.

Text.SourceString: It’s snowing again...guess it’s time to bundle up like a snowman.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s snowing again...guess it’s time to bundle up like a snowman.

Text.SourceString: I can’t feel my face.
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t feel my face.

Text.SourceString: Do we have enough firewood? It’s going to be a cold one tonight!
Text.LocalizedString: Do we have enough firewood? It’s going to be a cold one tonight!

Text.SourceString: Everything is covered in snow.
Text.LocalizedString: Everything is covered in snow.

Text.SourceString: Ooh, look at that snowflake! So pretty!
Text.LocalizedString: Ooh, look at that snowflake! So pretty!

Text.SourceString: Whoa, did you hear that thunder? That was a loud one, {ParentLabel}!
Text.LocalizedString: Whoa, did you hear that thunder? That was a loud one, {ParentLabel}!

Text.SourceString: Storm’s rolling in...better stay inside where it’s safe and dry.
Text.LocalizedString: Storm’s rolling in...better stay inside where it’s safe and dry.

Text.SourceString: The storm’s pretty intense today. Hope we don’t lose power!
Text.LocalizedString: The storm’s pretty intense today. Hope we don’t lose power!
